        "text_tgMGVm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Allow the garment and transfer to cool down completely before peeling. This step is crucial, as peeling the foil while it’s warm can result in incomplete adhesion or damage to the design.</p><p>Once the design is fully cooled, carefully peel off the foil sheet. This reveals the metallic design now adhered to the garment.</p>",
