            "text": "<p>To lock in the design and improve durability, press the garment again using the same settings: <strong>330°F</strong>, <strong>20 seconds</strong>, and <strong>firm pressure</strong>. This step enhances the bond and ensures a long-lasting finish.</p><p>Use a lint roller to gently remove any excess foil fragments from the garment. This final step ensures a clean, professional appearance.</p><p>With these steps, you can confidently create stunning, metallic designs that elevate your garments to a retail-quality finish. Gold and Silver Foil DTF Transfers are perfect for logos, accents, and single-color designs that demand a touch of luxury.</p>",
